  i A setTimeout created in an effect must be cleared in the cleanup function.
  
  i Not clearing the timeout can cause memory leaks and trigger state updates on an unmounted component.
  
  i Return a cleanup function from the effect that calls clearTimeout with the timeout ID.
  
  i This rule belongs to the nursery group, which means it is not yet stable and may change in the future. Visit https://biomejs.dev/linter/#nursery for more information.
  

